I’m excited for my union friends that the strike is over! 🥳
What many people don’t know is that I’m SAG-eligible and have been for a while. But even with being SAG-e, the strike affected me as well as many others (not in the union). On a few occasions, I went out on the picket lines in solidarity. It was such an amazing community to witness and be a part of… and I hope to be a part of the union when “the time is right”. 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻
I know in the coming days, the members will review and vote. I have no doubt that they will make the best decision for themselves as well as for those of us to follow. 💪🏻
Let’s get back to work! 🙌🏻
